<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    {{> head}}
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.4/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    {{> header}}
    {{> start}}

    <ul>
      <li>資料來源：世界銀行</li>
      <li>點擊圖示可以查詢更多資訊</li>
      <li>備註：僅顯示各國主要單一債務，非所有債務總和，各國外債列表可<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E5%80%BA%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8">參考這裡</a></li>
    </ul>

	<div class="ui buttons">
	  <button id="gdp" class="ui button" onclick="GDP()">GDP</button>
	  <button id="debt" class="ui button" onclick="DEBT()">債務</button>
	</div>
	<div style="width: 100%; ">
		<div style="float: left;">
      <div id="graph"></div>
			<div style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
			<label for="year">年份:</label>
			<input type="text" id="year" style="border:0; color:#f6931f; font-weight:bold; " />
			</div>
			<div id="slider"></div>
		</div>
		<div id="bar"></div>
  </div>
  {{> end}}
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.4/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdn.firebase.com/js/client/2.2.1/firebase.js"></script>
	<script src="http://labratrevenge.com/d3-tip/javascripts/d3.tip.v0.6.3.js"></script>
	<script src="./index.js"></script>
  {{> footer}}
  </body>
</html>
